history.content:
I am planning on having a class at the same time Spring 2019. They always have webcasts so I figured I can just use that instead of going to lecture, but do they generally allow exam rescheduling?

Edit: Resolved. Just saw pinned post stating that instructors will not accommodate time conflicts.
history.subject: Does CS 170 generally allow exam rescheduling?
